PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,FThe school's headteacher Mrs Amelia
OL,8,FMcIlroy, said: "It is with great
OL,9,Fsadness that we are confirming the
OL,10,Floss of Juliette, a much loved and
OL,11,Ftreasured member of our school
OL,12,Fcommunity. Juliette was a student at
OL,13,Four school for seven years.
OL,15,F"She was incredibly kind, thoughtful
OL,16,Fand intelligent and she loved our
OL,17,Fschool and was very happy here.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,F"Juliette embraced everything that
OL,8,Fschool had to offer with great
OL,9,Fenthusiasm and joy and her humour and
OL,10,Fpositivity were captivating.
OL,12,F"She was a genuinely caring and
OL,13,Fattentive listener, a true friend -
OL,14,Fwho listened with warmth, respect and
OL,15,Fsincere interest to her peers and to
OL,16,Four staff.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
