FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,F"In short, she was a lovely girl - her
OL,8,Fbeautiful smile, her loving nature and
OL,9,Fher sense of fun will be hugely
OL,10,Fmissed. We are all devastated. Our
OL,11,Flove and thoughts are with her family
OL,12,Fand friends at this terribly sad time.
OL,14,F"Our priority now is the safety and
OL,15,Fwell-being of all members of our
OL,16,Fschool community and we are continuing
OL,17,Fto work closely with UKHSA."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
