CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,FIt follows the death of a Kent
OL,8,FUniversity student, which was
OL,9,Fconfirmed by the institute on Sunday
OL,10,Fnight. Another 11 people are
OL,11,Funderstood to be seriously ill in
OL,12,Fhospital.
OL,14,FA spokesperson said: "We are deeply
OL,15,Fsaddened to confirm that one student
OL,16,Ffrom the University of Kent has died
OL,17,Ffollowing a case of invasive
OL,18,Fmeningitis.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,F"Our thoughts are with the student's
OL,8,Ffamily, friends and the wider
OL,9,Funiversity community at this extremely
OL,10,Fdifficult time.
OL,12,F"The safety of our students and staff
OL,13,Fremains our highest priority. We are
OL,14,Fworking closely with public health
OL,15,Fteams and are in touch with staff and
OL,16,Fstudents to ensure they get the advice
OL,17,Fand support they need. We will
OL,18,Fcontinue to monitor the situation and
OL,19,Fkeep our community informed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,F"We recognise that this is a very sad
OL,8,Fand worrying time for our community
OL,9,Fand we are doing everything we can to
OL,10,Foffer advice and support.
OL,12,F"This is a regional public health
OL,13,Fmatter and not specific to the
OL,14,FUniversity. The response is being led
OL,15,Fby the UKHSA and we are working with
OL,16,Fthem and partners as the situation
OL,17,Funfolds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
