OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,F"Known contacts of existing cases in
OL,8,Four community have been contacted and
OL,9,Fadvised on next steps. Students
OL,10,Fimpacted are being offered antibiotic
OL,11,Ftreatment on our Canterbury campus.
OL,13,F"We have contacted all our students
OL,14,Fand staff to ensure they have all the
OL,15,Flatest advice and support they need,
OL,16,Fand we will continue to update via
OL,17,Femail and social media.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
