PN,41109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,F"As a further precautionary measure
OL,8,Fthere will be no in person assessments
OL,9,For exams this week - students have
OL,10,Fbeen contacted directly with details
OL,11,Fon alternative arrangements."
OL,13,FMore than 30,000 young people are
OL,14,Fbeing contacted in the Canterbury area
OL,15,Ffollowing the meningitis outbreak.
OL,17,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,18,Fsaid it had been notified of 13 cases
OL,19,Fwith signs and symptoms of meningitis
OL,20,Ffrom Friday to Sunday in the
OL,21,FCanterbury area of Kent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
