OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,FThe specific strain of meningitis has
OL,8,Fnot yet been identified.
OL,10,FA local nightclub - Club Chemistry -
OL,11,Fin Canterbury, said it has been
OL,12,Fcontacted by officials to try and
OL,13,Ftrace people who may be affected.
OL,15,FIts owner, Louise Jones-Roberts, said
OL,16,Fit was closing for the rest of the
OL,17,Fweek following the deaths of two young
OL,18,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
