PN,41111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,FClub Chemistry said in a Facebook post
OL,8,Fon Monday afternoon: "We've made the
OL,9,Fdecision to close the venue for the
OL,10,Frest of this week.
OL,12,F"While we haven't been directed to do
OL,13,Fso, the safety and wellbeing of our
OL,14,Fcommunity, our guests and our staff
OL,15,Fcomes first ` always.
OL,17,F"We know this news may be worrying and
OL,18,Fwe are working closely with the UK
OL,19,FHealth Security Agency (UKHSA).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
