PN,41112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,F"We will share updates as soon as we
OL,8,Fhave them."
OL,10,FA UKHSA spokesperson said it was
OL,11,Farranging antibiotics for some
OL,12,Fstudents in the Canterbury area
OL,13,Ffollowing the outbreak.
OL,15,FThe organisation said it is working
OL,16,Fwith the University of Kent to
OL,17,F"provide advice letters to all 16,000
OL,18,Fstudents, advising on recent cases,
OL,19,Fsigns and symptoms, how to obtain
OL,20,Fantibiotics, and what to do if they
OL,21,Ffeel unwell."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
