PN,41113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,FLong queues of people waiting for
OL,8,Fantibiotics have continued to snake
OL,9,Faround the University of Kent campus,
OL,10,Ffollowing the death of a student from
OL,11,Fthe illness.
OL,13,FMany people are wearing face masks and
OL,14,Fstanding apart in scenes reminiscent
OL,15,Fof the Covid pandemic.
OL,17,FNot all 16,000 students at the
OL,18,Funiversity will be given antibiotics.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
