PN,41114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,FYou can read more about the advice
OL,8,Fissued to University of Kent students
OL,9,Fhere.
OL,11,FAmira Campbell, president of the
OL,12,FNational Union of Students, said: "We
OL,13,Fare saddened to hear of the deaths,
OL,14,Fthose who are hospitalised and the
OL,15,Fyoung people who are unwell.
OL,17,F"Our thoughts are with their family,
OL,18,Ffriends and everyone at the University
OL,19,Fof Kent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
