FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,F"We encourage everyone who is
OL,8,Fconcerned to follow the advice being
OL,9,Fshared by health professionals.
OL,11,F"There is simply not enough awareness
OL,12,Fof meningitis, especially as young
OL,13,Fpeople head off to university.
OL,15,F"While we all expect the inevitable
OL,16,Ffreshers flu, there are deadly viral
OL,17,Fstrains also circulating, which
OL,18,Fstudents need to be protected against
OL,19,Fand aware of."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
