PN,41116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,FA "suspected case" of meningitis has
OL,8,Fbeen confirmed in a student at The
OL,9,FNorton Knatchbull School in Ashford.
OL,11,FHeadteacher, Ben Greene, released the
OL,12,Ffollowing statement: "We can confirm
OL,13,Fthat we have a student in Year 13 who
OL,14,Fis receiving medical care in hospital
OL,15,Fwith a suspected case of meningitis.
OL,17,F"We are taking precautionary steps as
OL,18,Fa school in line with UK Health
OL,19,FSecurity Agency guidance, including
OL,20,Fmeasures to enhance hygiene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G16/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,F"Our priority is to ensure the safety
OL,8,Fand wellbeing of all students and
OL,9,Fstaff, and we have communicated to all
OL,10,Fparents and carers so that they are
OL,11,Faware of the symptoms to look out for
OL,12,Fand have appropriate guidance.
OL,14,F"The school's pastoral team are
OL,15,Fworking closely our students to
OL,16,Fprovide care, reassurance and support.
OL,18,F"Our thoughts go out to those who have
OL,19,Ftragically died and their families."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G17/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
