PN,41118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,FLetters have also been sent to parents
OL,8,Fof children at the school.
OL,10,FA Canterbury school has advised
OL,11,Fparents on the symptoms of meningitis
OL,12,Fto look out for following the outbreak
OL,13,Fin Kent.
OL,15,FIn a letter to parents, Barton Court
OL,16,FGrammar School headteacher Jonathan
OL,17,FHopkins wrote: "We are aware that some
OL,18,Fsixth-form students socialise with
OL,19,Ffriends from other schools in the
OL,20,Flocal area and may have visited venues
OL,21,Fin the city in recent weeks.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G18/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
