PN,41119
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,F"At this time, we have not been
OL,8,Finformed that any Barton Court
OL,9,Fstudents have been diagnosed with
OL,10,Fmeningitis.
OL,12,F"We will be contacting the UKHSA South
OL,13,FEast health protection team to
OL,14,Fregister our concern and seek their
OL,15,Fguidance, and we will act immediately
OL,16,Fon any advice they provide."
OL,18,FThe letter lists symptoms of
OL,19,Fmeningitis to watch out for and
OL,20,Fadvises what to do if any appear.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G19/20
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
