PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773691869
OL,3,CSixth form student who died from
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak in Kent has been
OL,5,Cnamed
OL,7,F"I understand that this will be
OL,8,Fworrying for many of you. While cases
OL,9,Fsuch as this remain rare, awareness of
OL,10,Fthe symptoms and acting quickly are
OL,11,Fthe best protection," the letter added.
